1936;;Hollywood Boulevard;;American;;Robert Florey;;John Halliday, Robert Cummings, Marsha Hunt;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hollywood_Boulevard_(1936_film);;The film portrays, in a comic expose of gossip magazines of the time, has-been actor John Blakeford (Halliday) agreeing to write his memoirs for magazine publisher Jordan Winston (Gordon).<br><br>When Blakeford's daughter, Patricia (Hunt), asks him to desist for the sake of his ex-wife, Carlotta Blakeford (Marsh), he attempts to break his contract with Winston.